sections.text:
86-1067.Rules and regulations.

The commission shall adopt and promulgate rules and regulations necessary to carry out the 911 Service System Act.

SourceLaws 2018, LB993, § 16;R.S.1943, (2024), § 86-1029.03;Laws 2025, LB362, § 49.Effective Date: September 3, 2025
